## Installation

1. Open the AssetLib tab inside the Godot 4 editor.
2. Search for {{ spec.title }} SDK.
3. Download and install plugin.
4. Enable the plugin from Project -> Project Settings -> Plugins.

## Getting Started

The plugin automatically intializes itself using values from .env. You can also set them at runtime using the `set_endpoint()`, `set_project()`, `set_project_name()` and `set_self_signed()` methods.

### Quick Test connection to Appwrite server 

```gdscript
extends Node

func _ready():
    {{spec.title | caseUcfirst}}.ping()
```

